Type: Package
Package: edgemeta
Title: Estimation and Prediction for Random-Effects Meta-Analysis using Edgington's Method
Version: 1.0
Date: 2025-04-29
Authors@R: 
    person("David", "Kronthaler", , "david.kronthaler@uzh.ch", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0004-9778-0249"))
Description: Frequentist estimation and prediction for random-effects meta-analysis
    using Edgington's method for combining p-value functions, or equivalently, 
    confidence distributions. Uncertainty about parameter estimates is accounted
    for through confidence distributions from Edgington's method and from the
    generalized heterogeneity statistic.
